	<Title>
		Lack of sleep: Can it make you sick?
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		Lack of sleep can affect your immune system. Here&apos;s what you need to know.
	</Abstract>
	<Question>
		I&apos;m having trouble sleeping lately. Does this increase my chances of getting sick?
	</Question>
